    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I wonder if the key `length` makes an object \"array-like\". We had this problem before in facet values, but that was back when we were using lodash. \r\n\r\nIs there a reason you're using offset and length, and not regular pagination? If you want to set a default page for infinite hits, that can be done by setting the page value in `searchState`.",
